text: Guingamp is a commune. It is found in the region Bretagne in the Côtes-d'Armor department in the west of France. ==Sister cities== Guingamp is twinned with: * Shannon, Ireland, since 1991 * Aue, Germany, since 9 May 2011 ==Related pages== * En Avant de Guingamp ==References== Category:Communes in Côtes-d'Armor Category:Subprefectures in France
title: Guingamp
